<td width="600" height="50" colspan="3" align="center" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:18px;line-height:22px;color:#ea007a"><strong>THIS MONTH: BOOK ONTO YOUR NCS TRAINING!</strong></td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="center" valign="top"><img src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/staffing/Images/ncstc_hr_290914.jpg" width="550" height="22" border="0" style="display:block"></td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:20px;color:#222222">
		
			<table width="550" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tbody><tr>
			
			<td align="left" valign="top"><p>This month we'll be releasing our training dates for the summer, so look out for details on how you can book onto your relevant training sessions.</p>

<p>Previously, you've given us feedback on how we could do it better - you've asked us for shorter sessions and more updates on the programme and how it's changed, and we've listened!</p>

<p>New for this year, if you're returning for the second year in a row, you'll only be required to attend one full day of jam-packed training.</p>

<p>If this is your 3rd year (in a row), you will only need to attend one 3-hour evening session to catch up on changes to the NCS programme!</p><td>
			
						
			<td align="right" valign="top"><img src="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/assets/Untitled_design_(10).jpg" alt="" width="230" height="225" border="0"><br>
			<img src="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/assets/Untitled_design_(13).jpg" alt="" width="230" height="225" border="0"><br>
			
			</tr></tbody></table>
		</td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
